data.name: lstSourceFiles.ToolTip
data.value: You can drop a bunch of files or folders here. If you drag a list of mixed files and folders then the folders are ignored and only the files are taken. When draging only folders then all containing files are added (not recursively).

data.name: numericUpDownJobs.ToolTip
data.value: Number of jobs which are processed simultaneously. This does not take account of already multithreading capable encoders. Do not set to high if the encoder itself does multithreading, and do not set it higher than your logical CPU cores.
